    "description": "Join the Angel One Ventures Solutions family as a Senior Financial Analyst in Srinagar. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Angel One Ventures Solutions:\nAngel One Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Angel One Ventures Solutions!",
